metadata.name: Casa Malaparte
metadata.description:
Built on a cliff overlooking the Mediterranean Sea, Casa Malaparte -designed by Curzio Malaparte- is a beautiful example of Italian rationalism. Its stairs lead to the roof, where a woman is enjoying the views under the sun, in a peaceful scene away from the noise.
